OL,6,FShe said the matter was a "genuine
OL,7,Fmistake" from which she "did not make
OL,8,Fany gain", and that magistrates gave
OL,9,Fher the "lowest possible outcome".
OL,11,FThe Transport Secretary said in her
OL,12,Fstatement: "In 2013 I was mugged while
OL,13,Fon a night out. I was a young woman
OL,14,Fand the experience was terrifying.
OL,16,F"I reported it to the police and gave
OL,17,Fthem a list of what I believed had
OL,18,Fbeen taken ` including a work mobile
OL,19,Fphone that had been issued by my
OL,20,Femployer.
