OL,6,F"Some time later I discovered that the
OL,7,Fmobile in question had not been taken.
OL,8,FIn the interim I had been issued with
OL,9,Fanother work phone.
OL,11,F"The original work device being
OL,12,Fswitched on triggered police attention
OL,13,Fand I was asked to come in for
OL,14,Fquestioning. My solicitor advised me
OL,15,Fnot to comment during that interview
OL,16,Fand I regret following that advice.
