OL,6,F"The police referred the matter to the
OL,7,FCPS and I appeared before Southwark
OL,8,Fmagistrates. Under the advice of my
OL,9,Fsolicitor I pleaded guilty ` despite
OL,10,Fthe fact this was a genuine mistake
OL,11,Ffrom which I did not make any gain.
OL,13,F"The magistrates accepted all of these
OL,14,Farguments and gave me the lowest
OL,15,Fpossible outcome (a discharge)
OL,16,Favailable."
