OL,6,FMs Haigh has been Sheffield Heeley MP
OL,7,Fsince 2015 and held a number of shadow
OL,8,Fministerial and shadow cabinet roles
OL,9,Fbefore becoming Transport Secretary
OL,10,Fwhen Labour won the election in July.
OL,11,FBefore she entered politics she spent
OL,12,Ftime as a special constable.
OL,14,FIt is understood that it was a fraud
OL,15,Foffence and the incident was disclosed
OL,16,Fin full to Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer when she joined the shadow
OL,18,Fcabinet. The conviction is now spent.
