OL,6,FThe chair of the Conservative Party
OL,7,Fsaid the Prime Minister has "serious
OL,8,Fquestions" to answer about the matter.
OL,10,FNigel Huddleston said in a statement:
OL,11,F"These are extremely concerning
OL,12,Frevelations about the person
OL,13,Fresponsible for managing #30 billion
OL,14,Fof taxpayers' money.
OL,16,F"Keir Starmer has serious questions to
OL,17,Fanswer regarding what he knew and when
OL,18,Fabout the person he appointed as
OL,19,FTransport Secretary admitting to
OL,20,Fhaving misled the police."
